question: Show me all sommeliers and bartenders called Alex
sql_query1:
SELECT Professionals.FullName
FROM Professionals
WHERE (Professionals.Position = "Sommelier" OR Professionals.Position = "Bartender") AND Professionals.FullName LIKE "Alex %"
sql_query2:
SELECT Professionals.FullName
FROM Professionals
WHERE Professionals.Position = "Sommelier" OR Professionals.Position = "Bartender" AND Professionals.FullName LIKE "Alex %"
interpretation1: List all sommeliers with the first name of Alex and all bartenders with first name of Alex
interpretation2: Show all sommeliers and also show all bartenders with first name of Alex.
